# This tool has NO local .env. Credentials come from the repo-root .env
# (jami.studio/.env, gitignored), under its "## Framer Project Keys" block:
#
#   ## Framer Project Keys
#   Message AI
#   FRAMER_API_KEY=fr_...
#   FRAMER_PROJECT_URL=https://framer.com/projects/<id>?node=...
#   (one block per template: Message AI, Nouva, Kirimo, Noir, Synk)
#
# projects.config.mjs parses that block — one secrets file, no duplication.
# Per-project API key: Framer -> Site Settings -> General -> API keys.
# Per-project URL/id: framer.com/projects/<id> (project address bar).
